## Datenformat, das am besten passt

Empfohlen:

```text
monitoring/history/metrics.jsonl
```

mit Zeilen wie:

```json
{"timestamp":"2026-06-14T12:00:00Z","error_rate":0.021,"latency_ms":142,"quality_score":0.88}
```

Für Embeddings optional:

```text
monitoring/history/features.npy
```

mit Shape:

```text
(n_samples, n_dimensions)
```

oder JSONL:

```json
{"timestamp":"2026-06-14T12:00:00Z","embedding":[0.12,-0.03,0.44]}
```

